    SVC --> AUDIT[(Audit Log Store)]
    SVC --> AGENTS[(AI Agent Roster Source)]
    SVC --> OBS[Structured Logs / Metrics / Traces]
    OBS --> DASH[Monitoring Dashboard & Alerts]
